Create soft links to raw data using commands in misc.txt

Run genome_assembly.sh to assemble the PacBio reads with Canu

Run fastqc_illumina.sh to perform a quality control with FastQC on the Illumina reads

(optional) Run MultiQC using commands in misc.txt to generate a summary of the FastQC analysis

(optional) Generate a summary of the test results from the FastQC run  using commands in misc.txt

Run bwa_alignment.sh to align the PacBio assembly with the Illumina reads

Run pilon_improvement.sh to improve the assembly using the Illumina reads with Pilon
